// Base64 мқҙлҜём§ҖлҘј Neocitiesм—җ м—…лЎңл“ңн•ҳлҠ” н•ЁмҲҳ
async function processBase64Images(content) {
  if (!content || !content.ops) return content;
  
  const newOps = [];
  
  for (const op of content.ops) {
    if (op.insert && op.insert.image && op.insert.image.startsWith('data:image/')) {
      try {
        console.log('Processing Base64 image...');
        
        // Base64лҘј BlobмңјлЎң ліҖнҷҳ
        const base64Data = op.insert.image;
        const arr = base64Data.split(',');
        const mime = arr[0].match(/:(.*?);/)[1];
        const bstr = atob(arr[1]);
        let n = bstr.length;
        const u8arr = new Uint8Array(n);
        
        while (n--) {
          u8arr[n] = bstr.charCodeAt(n);
        }
        
        const blob = new Blob([u8arr], { type: mime });
        
        // Neocitiesм—җ м—…лЎңл“ң
        const neocitiesUrl = await uploadImageToNeocities(blob, mime);
        
        // мғҲлЎңмҡҙ op мғқм„ұ (Neocities URL мӮ¬мҡ©)
        newOps.push({
          insert: {
            image: neocitiesUrl
          }
        });
        
        console.log(`Image uploaded: ${neocitiesUrl}`);
        
      } catch (error) {
        console.error('Image upload failed:', error);
        // мӢӨнҢЁн•ң кІҪмҡ° мӣҗліё мң м§Җ
        newOps.push(op);
      }
    } else {
      newOps.push(op);
    }
  }
  
  return { ...content, ops: newOps };
}

// Neocitiesм—җ мқҙлҜём§Җ м—…лЎңл“ң
async function uploadImageToNeocities(blob, mimeType) {
  const apiToken = neocitiesApiToken;
  const siteName = 'dakimakura';
  
  if (!apiToken) {
    throw new Error('Neocities API token not found');
  }
  
  // кі мң н•ң нҢҢмқјлӘ… мғқм„ұ
  const timestamp = Date.now();
  const randomString = Math.random().toString(36).substring(2, 15);
  const extension = mimeType.split('/')[1];
  const fileName = `images/uploaded/${timestamp}_${randomString}.${extension}`;
  
  // FormData мғқм„ұ
  const formData = new FormData();
  formData.append('file', blob, fileName);
  
  // Neocities API нҳём¶ң
  const response = await fetch(`https://neocities.org/api/upload`, {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: {
      'Authorization': `Bearer ${apiToken}`
    },
    body: formData
  });
  
  if (!response.ok) {
    const errorData = await response.text();
    throw new Error(`Upload failed: ${response.status} ${errorData}`);
  }
  
  const result = await response.json();
  return `https://${siteName}.neocities.org/${fileName}`;
}

// Base64 мқҙлҜём§Җк°Җ мһҲлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқё
function hasBase64Images(posts) {
  for (const post of posts) {
