// нғңк·ё м ңм•Ҳ кё°лҠҘ (кё°мЎҙ нғңк·ём—җм„ң м¶”м¶ң)
function setupTagSuggestions() {
  const tagInput = document.getElementById('post-tags');
  const suggestions = document.getElementById('tag-suggestions');
  
  // кё°мЎҙ нҸ¬мҠӨнҠём—җм„ң лӘЁл“  нғңк·ё м¶”м¶ң
  function getAllExistingTags() {
    const posts = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('hamster_posts') || '[]');
    const allTags = new Set();
    
    console.log('All posts data:', posts);
    
    posts.forEach(post => {
      console.log('Post tags:', post.tags, 'type:', typeof post.tags);
      if (post.tags) {
        if (Array.isArray(post.tags)) {
          // л°°м—ҙмқё кІҪмҡ°
          post.tags.forEach(tag => {
            if (tag && tag.trim()) {
              allTags.add(tag.trim());
            }
          });
        } else if (typeof post.tags === 'string') {
          // л¬ёмһҗм—ҙмқё кІҪмҡ° (мүјн‘ңлЎң кө¬л¶„)
          const tags = post.tags.split(',').map(tag => tag.trim()).filter(tag => tag);
          tags.forEach(tag => allTags.add(tag));
        }
      }
    });
    
    console.log('Extracted tags:', Array.from(allTags));
    return Array.from(allTags);
  }
  
  // кё°мЎҙ нғңк·ё н‘ңмӢң
  function showExistingTags() {
    const existingTags = getAllExistingTags();
    if (existingTags.length > 0) {
      suggestions.innerHTML = `
        <div class="existing-tags-list">
          ${existingTags.map(tag => 
            `<span class="tag-button" onclick="addTag('${tag}')">${tag}</span>`
          ).join('')}
        </div>
      `;
      suggestions.style.display = 'block';
    } else {
      suggestions.innerHTML = `
        <div class="existing-tags-title">${i18nData?.write?.messages?.existingTags || 'кё°мЎҙ нғңк·ё'}</div>
        <div class="no-results">${i18nData?.write?.messages?.noTagsAvailable || 'мӮ¬мҡ© к°ҖлҠҘн•ң нғңк·ёк°Җ м—ҶмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.'}</div>
      `;
      suggestions.style.display = 'block';
    }
  }
  
  // мҙҲкё° лЎңл“ң мӢң кё°мЎҙ нғңк·ё н‘ңмӢң (н•ӯмғҒ ліҙмқҙлҸ„лЎқ)
  showExistingTags();
  
  tagInput.addEventListener('input', () => {
    const value = tagInput.value.toLowerCase();
    const existingTags = getAllExistingTags();
    const currentTags = tagInput.value.split(',').map(t => t.trim()).filter(t => t);
    
    if (value.length > 0) {
      const filteredTags = existingTags.filter(tag => 
        tag.toLowerCase().includes(value) && !currentTags.includes(tag)
      );
      
      if (filteredTags.length > 0) {
        suggestions.innerHTML = `
          <div class="filtered-tags-title">${i18nData?.write?.messages?.searchResults || 'кІҖмғү кІ°кіј:'}</div>
          <div class="filtered-tags-list">
            ${filteredTags.slice(0, 10).map(tag => 
              `<span class="tag-button" onclick="addTag('${tag}')">${tag}</span>`
            ).join('')}
          </div>
        `;
        suggestions.style.display = 'block';
      } else {
        suggestions.innerHTML = `<div class="no-results">${i18nData?.write?.messages?.noResults || 'кІҖмғү кІ°кіјк°Җ м—ҶмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.'}</div>`;
        suggestions.style.display = 'block';
      }
    } else {
      showExistingTags();
    }
  });
  
  // нҸ¬м»ӨмҠӨ мӢң кё°мЎҙ нғңк·ё лӢӨмӢң н‘ңмӢң
  tagInput.addEventListener('focus', () => {
    showExistingTags();
  });
}

function addTag(tag) {
  const tagInput = document.getElementById('post-tags');
  const currentTags = tagInput.value.split(',').map(t => t.trim()).filter(t => t);
  
  if (!currentTags.includes(tag)) {
    currentTags.push(tag);
    tagInput.value = currentTags.join(', ');
  }
  
  document.getElementById('tag-suggestions').style.display = 'none';
  tagInput.focus();
}


